Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)\blur3}{\3c&HA07437&}We do not even have any enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:38.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\blur3}{\3c&H9442CD&}We do not even have any enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)\blur3}{\3c&H9442CD&}Maybe there are other animals watching us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:41.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\blur3}{\3c&HD7C46E&}Maybe there are other animals watching us
