Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.06,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\blur3}{\3c&H1709C8&}Wear our favorite clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}{\3c&H1709C8&}We are at no doubt human beings
