Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:07.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)\blur3}{\3c&H764E1C&}They were born
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:08.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\blur3}{\3c&H030452&}They were born
